Evelyn Francisco https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Evelyn_Francisco 0 Evelyn Francisco (born Evelyn Barton; August 13, 1904, Little Rock, Arkansas – January 27, 1963, Corona, California) was a silent era film actress who began as a bathing beauty. Her sister, Betty Francisco, was also a movie star.
